instalando o tema flat-remix

instale os pacotes:
sudo dnf install glib2-devel ImageMagick

habilitar o gnome-themes
https://extensions.gnome.org/

vรก para o diretorio do usuario e baixe os temas:

git clone https://github.com/daniruiz/flat-remix

git clone https://github.com/daniruiz/flat-remix-gtk

crie a pasta local
mkdir -p ~/.icons && mkdir -p ~/.themes

copie os temas para as pastas criadas
cp -r flat-remix* ~/.icons/ && cp -r flat-remix-gtk* ~/.themes/


gsettings set org.gnome.shell.extensions.user-theme name "Flat-Remix-Blue-Light"

reboot

altere os temas com gnome-tweaks
